<FlowDocument PagePadding="13" AllowDrop="True" xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation" xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml">

<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">This sample illustrates about visualization of OLAP data through OlapChart and OlapGrid embedded in OlapClient control. Several properties are exposed to handle OlapReport manipulations, filtering, sorting and toggling sub-element's visibility.</Paragraph>
<Paragraph TextAlignment="Center"><Image Source="images/OlapClient Configuration Demo.png" Stretch="None" /></Paragraph>
<Paragraph TextAlignment="Center" FontFamily="Cambria" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="14">OlapClient configured with report manipulations, filtering, sorting and toggling sub-element's visibility</Paragraph>

<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}">Features:</TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>

<List Margin="20,20,0,0">
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Provides support for plotting OLAP data into Chart and Grid of OlapClient.</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Provides support for drilling row and column elements.</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Provides support for creating a new report.</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Provides support for loading an existing report.</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Provides support for saving report.</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Provides support for removing and renaming selected reports.</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Provides support for filtering and sorting using respective dialogs to filter and sort OLAP data.</Paragraph><Paragraph /></ListItem>
<ListItem><Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Provides support for toggling the visibility of sub-controls in OlapClient.</Paragraph></ListItem>
</List>

</FlowDocument>